&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;BDtexte&quot;&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Organisation sociale&lt;/b&gt; plantation (moisissure et 1-6 &lt;a class=&quot;pagelink&quot; href=&quot;Zombi-Humain.html&quot; title=&quot;Zombi humain&quot;&gt;zombis&lt;/a&gt;)
